  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Society beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.0N8TtGSk5enoLBZ8]{Eye for Numbers}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.P9HCz0uR6xPHuw72]{Multilingual}</li><li>When expert: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Wb3FHiDuY6Nuc0N0]{Hireling Manager}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.9OaLaP2DEUyJ6qEr]{Civic Acumen Path - Trained}</strong>: Your sharp vision enables you to gain information others can't perceive.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.eHjQVQW7pG7tNJzw]{Underworld Path - Trained}</strong>: You blend in particularily well in poor and crime-ridden areas.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.Fck2ke63fgIU4362]{Courtly Affairs Path - Trained}</strong>: Conversing with nobility and the leading caste is second nature to you.</li></ul>",
